================================================================================
Reverse-engineering notice
================================================================================

The C# sources under src/Local_Wps_Vsto_v2/ were produced by automated
decompilation (ILSpy 7.2.1) of the publicly distributed binary
"Local_Wps_Vsto.dll" shipped in "公文高手Wps插件单机版2.4.1.exe", followed by
human-applied corrections to make the result compile under csc.exe v4.0.30319,
and human-applied modifications to:

  1. force "UserUtil.IsVip()" and "UserUtil.HasLogin()" to always return true
  2. rebrand the user-visible label from 「公文高手」 to 「公文助手」

This is interoperability-oriented reverse engineering of a binary whose
original online activation services have been discontinued. We make no claim
to the original product name, original UI design, or original template
artworks contained in template/*.docx — these remain the intellectual
property of the original「公文高手」development team. If you are a rights
holder and have concerns, please contact us via GitHub Issues and we will
respond promptly.
